url = (
    'https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/mobilenet_v1_1.0_224_frozen.tgz'
    )

mlmodel_path = os.path.join(TMP_MODEL_DIR, 'mobilenet_v1_1.0_224.mlmodel')
mlmodel = tf_converter.convert(tf_model_path=tf_model_path, mlmodel_path=
    mlmodel_path, output_feature_names=['MobilenetV1/Predictions/Softmax:0'
    ], input_name_shape_dict={'input:0': [1, 224, 224, 3]},
    image_input_names=['input:0'], red_bias=-1, green_bias=-1, blue_bias=-1,
    image_scale=2.0 / 255.0)
self._test_coreml_model_image_input(tf_model_path=tf_model_path,

    'MobilenetV1/Predictions/Softmax:0', img_size=224)
